  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868280/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764690892\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868280/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764690892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868280/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764690892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Welcome in the racing simulator game: Coins Collector Simulator! The game takes place in the city \"Collectorus\" where you will have complete freedom. Taxi driver or policeman, it doesn't matter here, you just have to collect all the coins! <br><br>Remember that your cars are powered by electricity, so they can be discharged fairly quickly if you don't power them.<br><br>Game Features:<br>- A big open-world style city<br>- 7 vehicles to choose from<br>- Collectable energy & coins<br>- Speedometer & battery<br>- 4 camera modes",
